name: Aiden
shortDescription: Aiden is a web app utilising tensorflow.js, browser-based Machine Learning library, to enable accessible physiotherapy for the Visually Impaired and other people as well - talking through exercises by responding to users' postures in real-time.
longDescription: Aiden is a web app utilising tensorflow.js, browser-based Machine Learning library, to enable accessible physiotherapy for the Visually Impaired and other people as well - talking through exercises by responding to users' postures in real-time.
